<i>noun</i>: 벌 [벌ː] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>벌 [벌ː]</dt><br>
<dd>bee</dd><br>
<dd>꽃에서 꿀과 꽃가루를 모아 저장하며, 몸 끝에 독이 있는 침이 달린 날아다니는 곤충.</dd><br>
<dd>A flying insect with a venomous sting at the end of its body, which gathers nectar and pollen from flowers and stores them.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>